<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Heading Tag Example</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Main Title: Welcome to My Website</h1>
    <p>This is an example of a heading tag in HTML. The headings are shown from largest to smallest.</p>

    <h2>Section 1: About Us</h2>
    <p>We are a company dedicated to providing quality services.</p>

    <h3>Subsection 1.1: Our Mission</h3>
    <p>Our mission is to deliver the best products to our customers.</p>

    <h4>Subsection 1.1.1: Core Values</h4>
    <p>We value honesty, commitment, and customer satisfaction.</p>

    <h5>Subsection 1.1.1.1: Honesty</h5>
    <p>Honesty is the foundation of our work culture.</p>

    <h6>Smallest Heading Example</h6>
    <p>This is the smallest heading in HTML.</p>

</body>
</html>
